  </p>
  <p>In the event that you complete a survey form for participation in survey prize draw by providing information which is not necessary for participation in the prize draw (such information may vary depending on the prize draw) VALAMAR RIVIERA will, nonetheless, be able to use all such depersonalised data for statistical purposes.
